{
  "id": "69f4120bb5336d1b73c003d1",
  "title": "ヒエラルキーの外に立とうとする思想",
  "created": 1777603088,
  "updated": 1777638900,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f4120bb5336d1b73c003d1",
      "text": "ヒエラルキーの外に立とうとする思想",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777603088,
      "updated": 1777603088
    },
    {
      "id": "69f4120e00000000003845de",
      "text": "社会的な[ヒエラルキー]の外側に立とうとする[思想]。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777603088,
      "updated": 1777604424
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41750000000000016f469",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604432,
      "updated": 1777604432
    },
    {
      "id": "69f4120f00000000003845df",
      "text": "どういうのがあるだろう？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777603088,
      "updated": 1777604432
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41751000000000016f46a",
      "text": " 社会的ヒエラルキー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604433,
      "updated": 1777604450
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41762000000000016f46b",
      "text": " \t上と下の関係",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604450,
      "updated": 1777604450
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41768000000000016f46c",
      "text": " \t成功者と失敗者",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604455,
      "updated": 1777604461
    },
    {
      "id": "69f4176e000000000016f46d",
      "text": " \t勝者と敗者",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604461,
      "updated": 1777604466
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41773000000000016f46e",
      "text": " \t\tこれで[ヒエラルキー]を作ろうとするのって[トーナメント]みたいになってる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604467,
      "updated": 1777604495
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41727000000000016f468",
      "text": "  支配と非支配",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604391,
      "updated": 1777604516
    },
    {
      "id": "69f417a5000000000016f470",
      "text": "  学級ヒエラルキー",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604517,
      "updated": 1777604530
    },
    {
      "id": "69f417b4000000000016f471",
      "text": "\t社会的ヒエラルキーの外側に立つ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604532,
      "updated": 1777604561
    },
    {
      "id": "69f417bb000000000016f472",
      "text": "\t\t自分の価値観に従う",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604539,
      "updated": 1777604548
    },
    {
      "id": "69f417d5000000000016f473",
      "text": "\t\t2つ以上ヒエラルキーがある（派閥がある）場面を想像すると、コウモリをすることかもしれない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604565,
      "updated": 1777605110
    },
    {
      "id": "69f41822000000000016f474",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/50d0a72e17074c27567754c1816204ce]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777604641,
      "updated": 1777605098
    },
    {
      "id": "69f419eb000000000016f476",
      "text": "   [鳥と獣とコウモリ][inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777605098,
      "updated": 1777637815
    },
    {
      "id": "69f499a600000000004d20ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777637799,
      "updated": 1777637799
    },
    {
      "id": "69f419d0000000000016f475",
      "text": "「[恋愛ゲームから降りられて本当に良かった]」が関連しそう[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777605071,
      "updated": 1777607230
    },
    {
      "id": "69f417a4000000000016f46f",
      "text": "[ヒエラルキーの外に立つ][inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777604516,
      "updated": 1777638558
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49c9f00000000004d20b6",
      "text": "あとなんだっけ、コミュニティの橋渡しみたいな役のやつ、、[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777638560,
      "updated": 1777638739
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49d6e0000000000011815",
      "text": " [/nishio/移動する人が定住する人をむすびつける]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777638767,
      "updated": 1777638767
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49d5700000000004d20b9",
      "text": "  なんかこの辺の話",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777638744,
      "updated": 1777638750
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49b7400000000004d20b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777638261,
      "updated": 1777638261
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49c670000000000011810",
      "text": " 土俵という言い方がありそう[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777638504,
      "updated": 1777638697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49c46000000000001180f",
      "text": "  [相手の土俵で勝負]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777638471,
      "updated": 1777638697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49c3d000000000001180d",
      "text": " \t[別の土俵で戦うスタイル]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777638462,
      "updated": 1777638697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49d240000000000011814",
      "text": "\t「狭い界隈で有名なだけの人の勘違い」的なイヤミをツイッターでたまに見る",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777638693,
      "updated": 1777638900
    },
    {
      "id": "69f49d890000000000011817",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777638801,
      "updated": 1777638801
    }
  ]
}